- **Error Handling**: Implement checks to confirm the availability of resources before attempting to perform actions.
- **Exploration**: Use broader commands to explore the environment fully to uncover any hidden resources or entities.

The interaction has reached a standstill, and I will conclude my engagement here. I look forward to future opportunities to interact in a more resource-rich and dynamic environment. Thank you for your patience, and I hope for a more engaging experience next time!
